{"tid":2383442,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"菠蘿會黃國健:期待國藥疫苗盡快來港","createTime":"2021-01-28T02:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T02:12:28.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"01d3833db47afe63d99b07ad87d6f8299c6fa51d","tid":2383442,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:02:22.000Z","msg":"工聯會立法會議員黃國健表示，一直以來，國家傾力支持香港的抗疫工作，而有效抗疫，注射疫苗是重要一環，早前特區政府宣布將會購入內地生產的科興疫苗，不知什麼原因，完全沒有下文，鑑於很多市民表示只對內地生產的疫苗有信心，日前全國港區人大代表聯署，要國家供應內地正注射的國藥疫苗，今次得到習主席的支持，希望國家能夠回應港人的訴求，盡快讓國藥疫苗來港。"},{"pid":"a6311f7982afcc7df87aa273ea96b02c1b9b8b4f","tid":2383442,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:04:44.000Z","msg":"支持全體工聯會會員接種科興疫苗<br />\n仲要規定接種咗科興疫苗先有資格上工聯會興趣班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb89267ddcf5ecbd2e0b562dd570baf24aef18a","tid":2383442,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6311f7982afcc7df87aa273ea96b02c1b9b8b4f","tid":2383442,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:04:44.000Z","msg":"支持全體工聯會會員接種科興疫苗<br />\n仲要規定接種咗科興疫苗先有資格上工聯會興趣班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:10:34.000Z","msg":"所有工聯會屬會會員都要打大陸針"},{"pid":"f919db8ca51196eb078f5cd97307d1f04e850073","tid":2383442,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:11:04.000Z","msg":"班友係咪用科興垃圾凸顯企央果隻好D，逼9人打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2943d609ab1101c4d5b34f3f28c680d8060966","tid":2383442,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T02:11:11.000Z","msg":"鑑於很多市民表示只對內地生產的疫苗有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse